{"tid":2193284,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"港人被困！求救！可唔可以經菲律賓轉機返香港？","createTime":"2020-09-07T16:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T19:33:44.000Z","uid":85236,"like":5,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"695fd78c6eefae29e462270c3af15c9e2460a94d","tid":2193284,"uid":85236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"求巴打絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老豆被困巴布亞新幾內亞，要飛返香港<br />\n<br />\n最方便係經菲律賓轉機，但菲律賓唔比入境，不過唔知可唔可以轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟搵左全日了，各個航空公司、衛生署都交波。<br />\n能力有限，希望有經驗巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預計行程<br />\n9月27日<br />\n     <br />\nLAE（巴新）&mdash;&gt;POM（巴新）&mdash;&mdash;&gt;MNL（馬尼拉）&mdash;&mdash;&gt;HKG<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇人知MNL T1去T3 轉機洗唔洗出入境，如果要再出入境就大鑊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b255194378eba10b94aade091e1b825dc516b5d","tid":2193284,"uid":85236,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"救爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f6cf2fdb9ba176957be27befe16af313deee08","tid":2193284,"uid":85236,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"負評狗出嚟隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58dc8cef314a18e2f307a4bfbd6deda2f4eecf6","tid":2193284,"uid":9435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"T1 T3好似兩個地方黎"},{"pid":"f344a099b0915031cf58312badb999943f165d4c","tid":2193284,"uid":85236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47a3fba4885ca33d67d09740115a8605cb8ba451","tid":2193284,"uid":198591,"like":13,"dislike":4